<Author>swigo
<Content>The nightmare! The hotel staff were absolutly insolent. The room that we got hadn't got window. There were impossible to smoke there and the bed was covered with disposable (!) sheets and blankets. There were children shouting all the night and all about that hotel like a nightmare. The most horrible thing was absence of bath and shower. And wash basin was very-very small. If you want to feel yourself like in prison - you can choose this hotel.Thnks God we slept there only 1 night and were glad to escape that place.ps We were so shoked after all that even didn't make any fotos of this hotel. 
